==English==
===Verb===
'''[[blow]] a [[gasket]]'''
#{{idiom}} To become very [[angry]] or [[upset]].
#:''When the teacher presented Hisato's dad a bad report card at the Parent/Teacher Conference, he '''blew a gasket''' at Hisato when he got home.''

